  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SISYPHE</strong> is an adventure game about a square that yearns to be a circle. Chip off pieces of the square at certain points along the journey, and climb a mountain in search of <strong>renewal</strong>. You'll walk and climb through <strong>seven</strong> visually distinct areas on your way up the mountain path. <br><br><strong>DISCLAIMER: The players physics have been heavily changed. The player is much faster and jumps higher than shows here. If you're on the fence because of how slow it looks, don't worry.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125820/extras/004d8d824af5a34621566bf9be5b903f.poster.avif?t=1742654469\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125820/extras/004d8d824af5a34621566bf9be5b903f.webm?t=1742654469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125820/extras/004d8d824af5a34621566bf9be5b903f.mp4?t=1742654469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SISYPHE</strong> is mainly an <strong>interactive art piece</strong>. It's a beautiful, casual climbing game that prioritizes <strong>atmosphere</strong> and the journey. SISYPHE keeps a unique visual style that embodies the feel and soul of the square's voyage. Listen to a beautiful soundtrack by <strong>Pierre Scheuer</strong> (PeterBarn) and creator <strong>Lucas Ljunggren</strong> along the way. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125820/extras/fe67e1e5a7d6e1aec1308004304bfd6a.poster.avif?t=1742654469\" width=692 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125820/extras/fe67e1e5a7d6e1aec1308004304bfd6a.webm?t=1742654469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125820/extras/fe67e1e5a7d6e1aec1308004304bfd6a.mp4?t=1742654469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore a gorgeous world</strong> of climbing possibilites. <strong>No</strong> invisible walls, <strong>no</strong> restrictions, climb anywhere you can. Find large artifacts and statues along the way, a good place to take the atmosphere in and stare at the <strong>incredible</strong> landscapes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125820/extras/2510d7609405e8bdec509642a60603c8.poster.avif?t=1742654469\" width=656 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125820/extras/2510d7609405e8bdec509642a60603c8.webm?t=1742654469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125820/extras/2510d7609405e8bdec509642a60603c8.mp4?t=1742654469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore <strong>SISYPHE</strong>, the beautiful, casual climbing game about the <strong>square</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125820/extras/411e3bc0d065fdfcd96598719629dff6.poster.avif?t=1742654469\" width=696 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125820/extras/411e3bc0d065fdfcd96598719629dff6.webm?t=1742654469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125820/extras/411e3bc0d065fdfcd96598719629dff6.mp4?t=1742654469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SISYPHE</strong> is an adventure game about a square that yearns to be a circle. Chip off pieces of the square at certain points along the journey, and climb a mountain in search of <strong>renewal</strong>. You'll walk and climb through <strong>seven</strong> visually distinct areas on your way up the mountain path. <br><br><strong>DISCLAIMER: The players physics have been heavily changed. The player is much faster and jumps higher than shows here. If you're on the fence because of how slow it looks, don't worry.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125820/extras/004d8d824af5a34621566bf9be5b903f.poster.avif?t=1742654469\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125820/extras/004d8d824af5a34621566bf9be5b903f.webm?t=1742654469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125820/extras/004d8d824af5a34621566bf9be5b903f.mp4?t=1742654469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SISYPHE</strong> is mainly an <strong>interactive art piece</strong>. It's a beautiful, casual climbing game that prioritizes <strong>atmosphere</strong> and the journey. SISYPHE keeps a unique visual style that embodies the feel and soul of the square's voyage. Listen to a beautiful soundtrack by <strong>Pierre Scheuer</strong> (PeterBarn) and creator <strong>Lucas Ljunggren</strong> along the way. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125820/extras/fe67e1e5a7d6e1aec1308004304bfd6a.poster.avif?t=1742654469